        <p>Numbers of reads assembled to full-length sequences per library that were extracted by SortMeRNA (vertical axes) versus BBmap (horizontal axes), comparing different cutoff settings for SortMeRNA (vertical facets) versus BBmap (horizontal facets). The 1:1 line (gray) is added to each plot for reference. Download <inline-supplementary-material id="fS3" xlink:href="mSystems.00920-20-sf003.pdf" content-type="local-data">FIG S3, PDF file, 0.7 MB</inline-supplementary-material>.</p>
